<tr>
<th style="border:1px solid #CCC; border-top:3px solid #CCC; background:#F3F3F3;"><a href="/wiki/File:P_christianity.svg" class="image" title="P christianity.svg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/79/P_christianity.svg/10px-P_christianity.svg.png" width="10" height="9" border="0" /></a> <b><a href="/wiki/Portal:Christianity" title="Portal:Christianity">Christianity Portal</a></b></th>
